OL,3,CFirst look inside pub that closed its
OL,4,Cdoors suddenly 11 years ago
OL,6,FGranada Reports journalist Claire
OL,7,FHannah was with the residents as they
OL,8,Fopened the door for the first time
OL,10,FA pub at the heart of a community
OL,11,Fwhich shut its doors more than a
OL,12,Fdecade ago will now re-open - after
OL,13,Fthe community rallied together to buy
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,FThe Golden Lion in the Cheshire
OL,17,Fvillage of Ashton Hayes closed without
OL,18,Fwarning on New Year's day 2013, with
OL,19,Fnot a single person passing through
OL,20,Fits front doors since.
