OL,6,F"We have it in community ownership.
OL,8,F"We now own it but we still need to do
OL,9,Fsome really effective fundraising to
OL,10,Fget enough money in to complete the
OL,11,Frefurbishment."
OL,13,FAs the Golden Lion was the only pub in
OL,14,Fthe village campaigners received a
OL,15,Fgovernment grant from the Levelling Up
OL,16,Ffund - but still needed to raise at
OL,17,Fleast #180,000.
OL,19,FThey then used an initiative where
OL,20,Fpeople could buy shares in the pub,
OL,21,Fwith the landlord agreeing to sell.
