OL,4,Cdoors suddenly 11 years ago
OL,6,FMr Deymen continued: "We've had share
OL,7,Fapplications in from Australia, you
OL,8,Fdon't have to live in the village, you
OL,9,Fcan live anywhere and buy a share in
OL,10,Fthe Golden Lion pub."
OL,12,FKen Hartley has been on the committee
OL,13,Ffor more than 10 years.
OL,15,F"It's remarkable really, the condition
OL,16,Fthat it's in, it's amazing. I mean
OL,17,Fthere are empty bottles and glasses
OL,18,Fall over the place...we're truly
OL,19,Famazed!" said Mr Hartley.
