OL,6,F"This village has been so creative in
OL,7,Fdoing what's its doing and this will
OL,8,Fbe the third project that it's been
OL,9,Fsuccessful in.
OL,11,F"We had the shop and the second thing
OL,12,Fwe did was a recreational field, and
OL,13,Fthis is our third. We're a super
OL,14,Fvillage."
OL,16,FThough it's been bought to re-open as
OL,17,Fa pub, it's now their space to do
OL,18,Fwhatever they like with it.
