OL,6,F"It's crucial to the village that it
OL,7,Fhas a meeting point, whether people
OL,8,Fuse it long term, it's open for the
OL,9,Fvillage to decide what to do it...we
OL,10,Fcan do lots of things with it,"
OL,11,Fcontinued Mr Hartley.
OL,13,FCampaigners are hoping The Golden Lion
OL,14,Fwill be open by Christmas 2024, and
OL,15,Fare already planning the resurrect
OL,16,Fsome of the old menus for their
OL,17,Fopening night.
